name: Majesty of our Planets by Albert Bierstadt

metadata.name: Jupiter Over Over the Glacial Plains of Europa
metadata.description: "Jupiter Over the Glacial Plains of Europar" by Bierstadt is a dramatic and detailed depiction of the planet Jupiter and its famous swirling clouds from Europa. The painting shows the planet's stormy atmosphere, with the Great Red Spot visible in the center, and a multitude of other storms and vortices swirling across the surface.
